e model error in\nshallow flow regimes and have a lot of potential to increase the predictive\npower of shallow flow models, while keeping them computationally cost\nefficient.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Dec 2017 22:12:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Mar 2018 21:35:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-09"}
