holds in the mean inter-species\nscattering length is explicitly demonstrated. Under proper management\nconditions, stationary compactons and quasi-compactons are quite stable and\nrobust excitations that can survive on very long time scale. A parameter design\nand a possible experimental setting for observation of these excitations are\nbriefly discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Dec 2017 14:05:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-10"}
